column5: I seen in the flyer thier hunting appearl is 50%off. While I was at the one here in Barrie,they had thier Rocky and Colman suits there. Great deal for those that are looking for some new wears. I was going to buy,but I got enough and I would be in SSSOOOOOOOOOOOO much trouble, if I came home with more stuff.  The south end store had a great deal on the orange bib and coat for 100 bucks. Not the light stuff either.

Hey Bud......Thx. for the heads up.....Don't worry about catching any trouble,you can stash it over here.....Don't forget to buy things a little bigger,so you'll have something to grow into.......lol.....TC and tight lines all........Chuck....
Lots of yer size there Chuck.
Thanks for the heads up. I'm due for some new camo.
Rats, I thought it was up here.  Pam
Hey Pam,it,s in the flyer. Maybe you got the same sale,WAYYYYYYY, up there.
